definitions.definition: The residue left by a person's finger that can be made visible by a process such as powder dusting ; a latent fingerprint .
An underlying cause that can be inferred from statistical correlations ; factor .

main_definition: ( forensics ) The residue left by a person's finger that can be made visible by a process such as powder dusting ; a latent fingerprint .
